      "rationale": "Use error assessment is not required at MRL 2 for this Class II device application. Simulation setup was performed by experienced analysts following documented standard operating procedures. This factor is scoped out per MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
